name: Fashionista Charm Bracelet
description:
Made with bronze findings and semi-precious beads, this bracelets defines everything a fashionista will love. Charms include a functional locket placed in the center of the bracelet.

Semi-Precious Beads Include:

Agate Stones - highly valued as a talisman in ancient times and has been used as a traveler’s amulet for centuries. It is believed to bring good fortune, health, wealth and long life. As well as quenching thirst and preventing fevers, Persian magicians used agate to divert storms and athletes to increase vitality. It's also said to bring self-confidence by banishing fear. Some call its strange patterns 'cosmic caterpillar tracks'. Others' swear that wearing these beads can heighten the spiritual consciousness and balance the body's physical and mental states*

Amethyst - A "stone of change, protection & enlightenment". Enhances spiritual awareness, meditation, visualization, serenity & composure. Attracts good luck & love, calms & transforms. Shifts energies to the higher frequencies of both the spiritual & ethereal levels.*

Citrine - Balances & energizes, dissipates negative energy. Enhances personal power, emotional awareness, creativity & optimism. Stimulates abundance by assisting one to acquire wealth & to maintain a state of wealth.*

Coral - Facilitates intuition, imagination, and visualization & strengthens understanding of mysticism. Alleviates depression, quiets the emotions ands brings peace. Strengthens the connection to the harmonious energies of the universe.*

Lapis Lazuli - A "stone of protection and enlightenment". Assists with spiritual growth, intuitive perception and objectivity. Mentally calming, supports clarity & helps one to organize day to day activities. Enhances serenity, acceptance and dreams.* 

Rose Quartz - Known as the "Stone of Love". Rose Quartz soothes, comforts & reassures, bringing about deep inner healing. Gently removes negativity & attracts the energy of love bringing peacefulness & calm to relationships.*

Turquoise - An "anti-negativity stone" & general healer. Dispels negative energy & protects. Encourages self-realization and creative problem solving. Strengthens the body and energy field. Heals the spirit; soothes and brings peace of mind. Attracts love.

*Semi-precious stones descriptions taken from http://www.soularenergy.com/gemstones.htm and http://www.mrbead.com/MrBead/stonelist6.htm


PACKAGING:
All pieces are wrapped in ribbon and tissue and packaged in a local "banig" box with gold ribbon and pearl accent.


CARE NOTES:
This bracelet contains semi-precious stones, which might be prone to breakage if dropped. 

This bracelet is made of high quality bronze chain and findings, however, to prevent unwanted oxidation (darkening or fading), please store in the velvet pouch provided when not in use.

name: The Dreamer Necklace
description:
“A dreamer, I walked enchanted, and nothing held me back.”
Daphne du Maurier

From the Dainty Lily Collection

Tiny cloud pendant, made of gold-dipped material, can be purchased alone or attached to a thin, basic, gold-plated chain of your preferred length. All chains come with a lobster clasp closure with a 2-inch extension chain for easy adjusting convenience.

PACKAGING:
Dainty Lily Necklaces are attached to their respective cards and placed in a matching envelope with a velvet/cloth care pouch for safekeeping.

CARE INSTRUCTIONS:
This items is made of gold-plated delicate materials and must be handled with care. Please store properly when not in use to prevent oxidation and ageing.
